{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.1","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:1","prev_osis_id":"Jer.043.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Censures contre les Juifs retir\u00e9s en \u00c9gypte<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-30: cf. (J\u00e9 42; 43.) J\u00e9 7:17, etc. Mt 23:37. Job 15:20-26.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>La parole fut adress\u00e9e \u00e0 J\u00e9r\u00e9mie sur tous les Juifs demeurant au pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte, demeurant \u00e0 Migdol, \u00e0 Tachpan\u00e8s, \u00e0 Noph et au pays de Pathros, en ces mots:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.2","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:2","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.43.13","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 43:13","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.43.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.2","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:2","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Ainsi parle l\u2019\u00c9ternel des arm\u00e9es, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl: Vous avez vu tous les malheurs que j\u2019ai fait venir sur J\u00e9rusalem et sur toutes les villes de Juda; voici, elles ne sont plus aujourd\u2019hui que des ruines, et il n\u2019y a plus d\u2019habitants,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.3","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:3","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.1","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:1","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.3","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:3","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>\u00e0 cause de la m\u00e9chancet\u00e9 avec laquelle ils ont agi pour m\u2019irriter, en allant encenser et servir d\u2019autres dieux, inconnus \u00e0 eux, \u00e0 vous et \u00e0 vos p\u00e8res.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.4","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:4","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.2","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:2","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.4","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:4","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Je vous ai envoy\u00e9 tous mes serviteurs, les proph\u00e8tes, je les ai envoy\u00e9s d\u00e8s le matin, pour vous dire: Ne faites pas ces abominations, que je hais.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.3","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:3","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.5","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:5","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Mais ils n\u2019ont pas \u00e9cout\u00e9, ils n\u2019ont pas pr\u00eat\u00e9 l\u2019oreille, ils ne sont pas revenus de leur m\u00e9chancet\u00e9, et ils n\u2019ont pas cess\u00e9 d\u2019offrir de l\u2019encens \u00e0 d\u2019autres dieux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.6","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:6","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.4","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:4","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.6","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:6","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Ma col\u00e8re et ma fureur se sont r\u00e9pandues, et ont embras\u00e9 les villes de Juda et les rues de J\u00e9rusalem, qui ne sont plus que des ruines et un d\u00e9sert, comme on le voit aujourd\u2019hui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.7","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:7","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.7","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:7","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Maintenant ainsi parle l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu des arm\u00e9es, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl: Pourquoi vous faites-vous \u00e0 vous-m\u00eames un si grand mal, que de faire exterminer du milieu de Juda hommes, femmes, enfants et nourrissons, en sorte qu\u2019il n\u2019y ait plus de vous aucun reste?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.8","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:8","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.6","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:6","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.8","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:8","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Pourquoi m\u2019irritez-vous par les \u0153uvres de vos mains, en offrant de l\u2019encens aux autres dieux du pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte, o\u00f9 vous \u00eates venus pour y demeurer, afin de vous faire exterminer et d\u2019\u00eatre un objet de mal\u00e9diction et d\u2019opprobre parmi toutes les nations de la terre?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.9","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:9","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.7","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:7","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.9","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:9","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Avez-vous oubli\u00e9 les crimes de vos p\u00e8res, les crimes des rois de Juda, les crimes de leurs femmes, vos crimes et les crimes de vos femmes, commis dans le pays de Juda et dans les rues de J\u00e9rusalem?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.10","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:10","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.8","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:8","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.10","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:10","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Ils ne se sont point humili\u00e9s jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce jour, ils n\u2019ont point eu de crainte, ils n\u2019ont point suivi ma loi et mes commandements, que j\u2019ai mis devant vous et devant vos p\u00e8res.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.11","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:11","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.9","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:9","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.11","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:11","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi ainsi parle l\u2019\u00c9ternel des arm\u00e9es, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl: Voici, je tourne ma face contre vous pour faire du mal, et pour exterminer tout Juda.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.12","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:12","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.10","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:10","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.12","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:12","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Je prendrai les restes de Juda qui ont tourn\u00e9 le visage pour aller au pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte, afin d\u2019y demeurer; ils seront tous consum\u00e9s, ils tomberont dans le pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte; ils seront consum\u00e9s par l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e, par la famine, depuis le plus petit jusqu\u2019au plus grand; ils p\u00e9riront par l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e et par la famine; et ils seront un sujet d\u2019ex\u00e9cration, d\u2019\u00e9pouvante, de mal\u00e9diction et d\u2019opprobre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.13","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:13","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.11","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:11","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.13","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:13","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Je ch\u00e2tierai ceux qui demeurent au pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte, comme j\u2019ai ch\u00e2ti\u00e9 J\u00e9rusalem, par l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e, par la famine et par la peste.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.14","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:14","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.12","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:12","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.14","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:14","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Nul n\u2019\u00e9chappera, ne fuira, parmi les restes de Juda qui sont venus pour demeurer au pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte, avec l\u2019intention de retourner dans le pays de Juda, o\u00f9 ils ont le d\u00e9sir de retourner s\u2019\u00e9tablir; car ils n\u2019y retourneront pas, sinon quelques r\u00e9chapp\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.15","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:15","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.13","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:13","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.15","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:15","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Tous les hommes qui savaient que leurs femmes offraient de l\u2019encens \u00e0 d\u2019autres dieux, toutes les femmes qui se trouvaient l\u00e0 en grand nombre, et tout le peuple qui demeurait au pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte, \u00e0 Pathros, r\u00e9pondirent ainsi \u00e0 J\u00e9r\u00e9mie:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.16","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:16","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.14","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:14","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.16","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:16","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Nous ne t\u2019ob\u00e9irons en rien de ce que tu nous as dit au nom de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.17","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:17","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.15","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:15","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.17","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:17","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Mais nous voulons agir comme l\u2019a d\u00e9clar\u00e9 notre bouche, offrir de l\u2019encens \u00e0 la reine du ciel, et lui faire des libations, comme nous l\u2019avons fait, nous et nos p\u00e8res, nos rois et nos chefs, dans les villes de Juda et dans les rues de J\u00e9rusalem. Alors nous avions du pain pour nous rassasier, nous \u00e9tions heureux, et nous n\u2019\u00e9prouvions point de malheur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.18","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:18","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.16","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:16","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.18","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:18","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Et depuis que nous avons cess\u00e9 d\u2019offrir de l\u2019encens \u00e0 la reine du ciel et de lui faire des libations, nous avons manqu\u00e9 de tout, et nous avons \u00e9t\u00e9 consum\u00e9s par l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e et par la famine\u2026<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.19","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:19","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.17","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:17","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.19","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:19","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>D\u2019ailleurs, lorsque nous offrons de l\u2019encens \u00e0 la reine du ciel et que nous lui faisons des libations, est-ce sans la volont\u00e9 de nos maris que nous lui pr\u00e9parons des g\u00e2teaux pour l\u2019honorer et que nous lui faisons des libations?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.20","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:20","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.18","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:18","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.20","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:20","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>J\u00e9r\u00e9mie dit alors \u00e0 tout le peuple, aux hommes, aux femmes, \u00e0 tous ceux qui lui avaient fait cette r\u00e9ponse:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.21","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:21","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.19","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:19","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.21","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:21","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel ne s\u2019est-il pas rappel\u00e9, n\u2019a-t-il pas eu \u00e0 la pens\u00e9e l\u2019encens que vous avez br\u00fbl\u00e9 dans les villes de Juda et dans les rues de J\u00e9rusalem, vous et vos p\u00e8res, vos rois et vos chefs, et le peuple du pays?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.22","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:22","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.20","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:20","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.22","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:22","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel n\u2019a pas pu le supporter davantage, \u00e0 cause de la m\u00e9chancet\u00e9 de vos actions, \u00e0 cause des abominations que vous avez commises; et votre pays est devenu une ruine, un d\u00e9sert, un objet de mal\u00e9diction, comme on le voit aujourd\u2019hui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.23","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:23","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.21","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:21","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.23","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:23","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>C\u2019est parce que vous avez br\u00fbl\u00e9 de l\u2019encens et p\u00e9ch\u00e9 contre l\u2019\u00c9ternel, parce que vous n\u2019avez pas \u00e9cout\u00e9 la voix de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et que vous n\u2019avez pas observ\u00e9 sa loi, ses ordonnances, et ses pr\u00e9ceptes, c\u2019est pour cela que ces malheurs vous sont arriv\u00e9s, comme on le voit aujourd\u2019hui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.24","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:24","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.22","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:22","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.24","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:24","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>J\u00e9r\u00e9mie dit encore \u00e0 tout le peuple et \u00e0 toutes les femmes: \u00c9coutez la parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, vous tous de Juda, qui \u00eates au pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.25","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:25","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.23","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:23","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.25","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:25","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Ainsi parle l\u2019\u00c9ternel des arm\u00e9es, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl: Vous et vos femmes, vous avez d\u00e9clar\u00e9 de vos bouches et ex\u00e9cut\u00e9 de vos mains ce que vous dites: Nous voulons accomplir les v\u0153ux que nous avons faits, offrir de l\u2019encens \u00e0 la reine du ciel, et lui faire des libations. Maintenant que vous avez accompli vos v\u0153ux, ex\u00e9cut\u00e9 vos promesses,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.26","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:26","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.24","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:24","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.26","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:26","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>\u00e9coutez la parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, vous tous de Juda, qui demeurez au pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte! Voici, je le jure par mon grand nom, dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel, mon nom ne sera plus invoqu\u00e9 par la bouche d\u2019aucun homme de Juda, et dans tout le pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte aucun ne dira: Le Seigneur, l\u2019\u00c9ternel est vivant!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.27","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:27","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.25","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:25","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.27","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:27","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Voici, je veillerai sur eux pour faire du mal et non du bien; et tous les hommes de Juda qui sont dans le pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte seront consum\u00e9s par l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e et par la famine, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce qu\u2019ils soient an\u00e9antis.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.28","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:28","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.26","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:26","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.28","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:28","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Ceux, en petit nombre, qui \u00e9chapperont \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e, retourneront du pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte au pays de Juda. Mais tout le reste de Juda, tous ceux qui sont venus au pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte pour y demeurer, sauront si ce sera ma parole ou la leur qui s\u2019accomplira.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.29","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:29","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.27","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:27","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.29","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:29","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.044.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Et voici, dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel, un signe auquel vous conna\u00eetrez que je vous ch\u00e2tierai dans ce lieu, afin que vous sachiez que mes paroles s\u2019accompliront sur vous pour votre malheur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.30","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:30","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.28","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:28","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.30","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:30","prev_osis_id":"Jer.044.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.045.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.44.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Ainsi parle l\u2019\u00c9ternel: Voici, je livrerai Pharaon Hophra, roi d\u2019\u00c9gypte, entre les mains de ses ennemis, entre les mains de ceux qui en veulent \u00e0 sa vie, comme j\u2019ai livr\u00e9 S\u00e9d\u00e9cias, roi de Juda, entre les mains de Nebucadnetsar, roi de Babylone, son ennemi, qui en voulait \u00e0 sa vie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.44","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.45.1","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 45:1","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.45.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.44.29","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 44:29","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.44.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"